which uses the SOPHGO SG2000 SoC [2].

Link: https://milkv.io/duo-s [1]
Link: https://en.sophgo.com/sophon-u/product/introduce/sg200x.html [2]

Signed-off-by: Joshua Milas <josh.milas@gmail.com>
